\c 119 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 119\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Dubbii Waaqayyoo Isa Ulfina-Qabeessatti, Abboommii Isaattis Gammaduu
\m \bd 1\bd* Warri balleessaa malee deddeebi'an, warri akka seera Waaqayyootti jiraatan haa gammadan.
\m \bd 2\bd* Warri abboommii isaaf dhugaa ba'u eegan, warri garaa guutuudhaan Waaqayyoon barbaadan,
\m \bd 3\bd* warri jal'ina hin hojjenne, warri karaa isaa irra deddeebi'an haa gammadan.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ajaji kee ba'eessa ta'ee akka eegamu ati abboomteetta.
\m \bd 5\bd* Karaa ani seerrata kee eegu irratti, jabaadhee utuun dhaabadhee attaman jaalladha.
\m \bd 6\bd* Ija koo abboommii kee hundumaa irraa yoon buqqifachuu dhiise, ani hin yeellaasifamu.
\m \bd 7\bd* Firdii ati qajeelummaadhaan laattu yommuun baru, ani yaada qajeelaadhaan galata siif nan galcha.
\m \bd 8\bd* Ani seerrata kee nan eega, ati raawwattee ana hin dhiisin!
\m \bd 9\bd* Dargaggeessi maaliin adeemsa isaa qullaa'ummaatti eeguu danda'a? Akka dubbii keetti adeemsa isaa qajeelfachuudhaan eeggachuu in danda'a.
\m \bd 10\bd* Garaa koo guutuu sin barbaaddadha, abboommii kee irraa akkan kaadhu hin godhin!
\m \bd 11\bd* Akkan si hin yakkineef waan ati jette garaa koo keessa kaa'adheera.
\m \bd 12\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati jajamaa dha, seerrata kee na barsiisi!
\m \bd 13\bd* Wanta qajeelaa ta'ee afaan keetiin dubbatame, ani arraba kootiin tokko tokkoon nan hima.
\m \bd 14\bd* Akkuma ani sooruma hundumaatti gammadu, wanta abboommiin kee dhugaa ba'u duukaa bu'uutti nan gammada.
\m \bd 15\bd* Ajaja kee irra-deddeebi'ee itti nan yaada, karaa kee irraas ija hin buqqifadhu.
\m \bd 16\bd* Seerranni kee garaa na ciibsa, dubbii kees hin irraanfadhu.
\m \bd 17\bd* Garbicha keef wanta gaarii godhi! Ani nan jiraadha, dubbii kees nan eega.
\m \bd 18\bd* Wanta dinqisiisaa seera kee keessaa akkan argutti, ati ija koo anaaf bani!
\m \bd 19\bd* Ani biyya lafaa irratti orma, abboommii kee ana duraa hin dhoksin.
\m \bd 20\bd* Wanta qajeelaa ta'ee si duratti fudhatame, yeroo hundumaa yaaduu irraa kan ka'e lubbuun koo in bututti.
\m \bd 21\bd* Warra gad-dhiisatti jiraatan ati in ifatta, warri abboommii kee irraa kaatanis abaaramoo dha.
\m \bd 22\bd* Ani abboommii siif dhugaa ba'u eegeera; ati ga'oo fi tuffii ana irraa fuudhi!
\m \bd 23\bd* Gurguddoonni taa'anii ana irratti yoo dubbatan iyyuu, garbichi kee seerrata kee irra-deddeebi'ee itti in yaada.
\m \bd 24\bd* Abboommonni siif dhugaa ba'an garaa na ciibsu, isaan gorsituu koo ti.
\m \bd 25\bd* Ani lafatti nan maxxanfame, ati akka dubbii keetti lubbuu anatti deebisi.
\m \bd 26\bd* Ani jireenya koo keessatti waanan ta'e sitti himadheera atis deebii anaaf kenniteetta; seerrata kee immoo na barsiisi!
\m \bd 27\bd* Karaa ati ajajje na hubachiisi, yommus ani hojii kee isa dinqisiisaa irra-deddeebi'ee itti nan yaada.
\m \bd 28\bd* Ani gadda irraa kan ka'e taa'ee nan boo'a, ati akka dubbii keetti ol na kaasi.
\m \bd 29\bd* Karaa sobaa irra akka ani hin adeemneef na eegi, seera keetiinis araara na argachiisi!
\m \bd 30\bd* Ani karaa dhugaa fo'adheera, wanta qajeelaa ta'ee si duratti fudhatames of dura kaa'adheera.
\m \bd 31\bd* Wanta abboommiin kee dhugaa ba'utti maxxanee nan jiraadha, yaa Waaqayyo, akka ani yeellaasifamu hin godhin!
\m \bd 32\bd* Ati garaan koo gammadee akka hubatu goote, anis karaa ati abboomte irra nan kaadha.
\m \bd 33\bd* Karaa seerranni kee irra nama buusu na barsiisi yaa Waaqayyo! Inni bu'aa waan qabuuf, hamma dhumaatti isa nan eega.
\m \bd 34\bd* Seera kee akkan yaadaan qabuuf, garaa koo guutuudhaanis akkan isa eeguuf, hubannaa anaaf kenni.
\m \bd 35\bd* Daandii ati abboomte irra akkan adeemu godhi, innoo anatti in tola.
\m \bd 36\bd* Bu'aa dalgaa fi sassatuu irraa, garaa koo gara wanta abboommiin kee dhugaa ba'uufitti qabi.
\m \bd 37\bd* Ija koo wanta waa'ee hin baafne ilaaluu irraa jal'isi, karaa kee irrattis lubbuu anatti deebisi!
\m \bd 38\bd* Garbichi kee akka si sodaatuuf, wanta abdachiifte isaaf raawwadhu.
\m \bd 39\bd* Wanti qajeelaa ta'ee si duratti fudhatame gaarii waan ta'eef, ga'oo isa ani sodaadhu ana irraa deebisi!
\m \bd 40\bd* Kunoo, ani ajaja kee hawwaan nan eeggadha, qajeelummaa keetiin lubbuu anatti deebisi.
\m \bd 41\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, akka ati jettetti, gaarummaan kee, gargaarsi kee inni fayyisus anaaf haa dhufu,
\m \bd 42\bd* yoos isa anatti ga'isuuf deebii ga'u nan kenna, anoo dubbii kee nan amanadha.
\m \bd 43\bd* Dubbii dhugaa matumaa ana duraa hin fudhatin! Anoo wanta qajeelaa ta'ee si duratti fudhatame abdiidhaan nan eeggadha.
\m \bd 44\bd* Ani itti fufee, yeroo hundumaaf bara baraan seera kee nan eega.
\m \bd 45\bd* Ani ajaja kee argachuudhaaf waanan barbaaddadheef, iddoo bal'aa keessa nan deddeebi'a. 
\m \bd 46\bd* Abboommii isa siif dhugaa ba'us, mootota duratti nan dubbadha, hin yeella'us.
\m \bd 47\bd* Abboommiin kee inni ani jaalladhu, garaa na ciibsa.
\m \bd 48\bd* Abboommii kee isa ani jaalladhutti harka koo nan hiixadha, seerrata kees irra-deddeebi'ee itti nan yaada.
\m \bd 49\bd* Dubbii kee isa abdiidhaan akka ani eeggadhu goote, ana garbicha keetiif yaadadhu.
\m \bd 50\bd* Wanti ati jette lubbuu anatti in deebisa, kunis yeroon gad deebi'utti jajjabina koo ti.
\m \bd 51\bd* Warri gad-dhiisatti jiraatan baay'isanii anatti in qoosu, ani garuu seera kee irraa hin jal'anne.
\m \bd 52\bd* Wanta durii durii jalqabee si duratti qajeelaa ta'ee fudhatame yommuun yaadadhu, jajjabina nan argadha, yaa Waaqayyo.
\m \bd 53\bd* Jal'oonni seera kee waan dhiisaniif, aarii guddaatu na qabe.
\m \bd 54\bd* Mana isa ani akka kara-adeemaatti itti galu keessatti, seerranni kee faarfannaa anaaf ta'e.
\m \bd 55\bd* Halkan maqaa kee nan yaadadha, yaa Waaqayyo; seera kees nan eega.
\m \bd 56\bd* Ani ajaja kee akkan eeguuf, carraan anaaf kennameera.
\m \bd 57\bd* Ani dubbii kee eeguudhaaf, "Waaqayyo qooda koo ti" jedheera.
\m \bd 58\bd* Fuula ifaadhaan akka na ilaaltuuf, garaa guutuudhaan sin kadhadha; akka dubbii keetti araara anatti argisiisi!
\m \bd 59\bd* Waa'ee karaa isa ani irra adeemuu nan yaade, miilla koos gara abboommii isa siif dhugaa ba'uutti nan qajeelfadhe.
\m \bd 60\bd* Ani abboommii kee irraa hin seesu, isa eeguuf nan ariifadha.
