\m \bd 66\bd* Anoo abboommii kee amanadheera, hubannaa gaarii anaaf kenni, waa beekuus na barsiisi!
\m \bd 67\bd* Utuu ani hin rakkifamin dura karaa irraa goreen ture, amma garuu wanta ati jette nan eega.
\m \bd 68\bd* Ati gaarii dha, wanta gaariis in hojjetta, seerrata kee na barsiisi.
