\m \bd 167\bd* Ani abboommii siif dhugaa ba'u lubbuudhumaaf nan eega, baay'isees isa nan jaalladha.
\m \bd 168\bd* Karaan koo hundinuu si dura waan jiruuf, ajaja kee, wanta seerri kee siif dhugaa ba'us nan eega.
\m \bd 169\bd* Iyyati koo si bira anaaf haa ga'u, yaa Waaqayyo, akka dubbii keetti hubannaa anaaf kenni!
\m \bd 170\bd* Himati koo si bira anaaf haa dhufu, akka abdachiiftetti na oolchi.
\m \bd 171\bd* Ati seerrata kee waan na barsiiftuuf, afaan koo jajata gad jijjigsa.
\m \bd 172\bd* Abboommiin kee hundinuu qajeelaa waan ta'eef, arraba kootiin waa'ee dubbii kee nan faarfadha.
\m \bd 173\bd* Harki kee na gargaaruudhaaf qophaa'aa haa ta'u! Anoo ajaja kee fo'adheera.
\m \bd 174\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gargaarsa kee isa fayyisu hawwaan nan eeggadha, seerri kee immoo garaa na ciibsa.
\m \bd 175\bd* Lubbuun koo akka jiraattu godhi, isheenis si haa jajattu! Wanti qajeelaa ta'ee si duratti fudhatames ana haa gargaaru!
\m \bd 176\bd* Ani akka hoolaa badee karaa irraa nan kaadhe, abboommii kee garuu hin irraanfanne; kanaafis ati garbicha kee barbaadi.
